				{
					"dataType": "talent",
					"elementDisplay": "<p chunk_id=\"2c095b2d-6232-408c-9766-cfe33e3c1497\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-stat\"><strong><span class=\"color-span\">Prerequisite:</span></strong>\n<tooltip category=\"talent\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"stable-flight\" nexus=\"cosmererpg\">Stable Flight</tooltip> talent\n</p>\n<p chunk_id=\"069ea804-772b-492f-88b0-f1f2d9386c38\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-stat\"><strong><span class=\"color-span\">Act</span></strong><strong><span class=\"color-span\">ivation:</span></strong> <span aria-label=\"Always Active\" class=\"icon-font icon\" title=\"Always Active\">∞</span></p>\n<div chunk_id=\"2b2526c6-5784-489e-996a-49bf13f44958\" class=\"lore-block\" style=\"\">\n<p class=\"\"><em>You can infuse multiple allies with Gravitation at once.</em></p>\n</div>\n<p chunk_id=\"fdd584d0-ab92-457d-a16d-42d3bee211ea\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-body ParaOverride-2\">While not in combat, when you spend 1 <tooltip category=\"rule\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"investiture\" nexus=\"cosmererpg\">Investiture</tooltip> or more to infuse yourself or a willing character with a Basic Lashing, you can also infuse a number of additional willing characters up to your ranks in Gravitation. Each target must be within your reach. These infusions last for the duration of the original infusion and require no additional Investiture to create or maintain.</p>",
