				{
					"dataType": "talent",
					"elementDisplay": "<p chunk_id=\"e7ab6af4-696b-4fc8-9f75-d972dce5df36\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-stat\"><strong><span class=\"color-span\">Prerequisite:</span></strong>\n<tooltip category=\"talent\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"gravitational-slam\" nexus=\"cosmererpg\">Gravitational Slam</tooltip> talent\n</p>\n<p chunk_id=\"f98ad78d-4320-4737-a8bc-016b0f03dde2\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-stat\"><strong><span class=\"color-span\">Act</span></strong><strong><span class=\"color-span\">ivation:</span></strong> <span aria-label=\"Two Actions\" class=\"icon-font icon\" title=\"Two Actions\">2</span></p>\n<div chunk_id=\"84eeb9c9-639a-46a1-a67d-b1db128c50db\" class=\"lore-block\" style=\"\">\n<p class=\"\"><em>You apply multiple Basic Lashings to an object, launching it with several times the force of gravity.</em></p>\n</div>\n<p chunk_id=\"3662fafb-20b2-4d78-b8f2-3df849c3d01b\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-body\">You touch an unattended object of a size you can affect with your ranks in Gravitation, then you propel that object at a target in your line of effect, spending Investiture equal to the distance to that target divided by your gravitation rate (rounded up).</p>\n<p chunk_id=\"93d2d7e3-a221-4bd4-855f-950f567ce468\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-body ParaOverride-2\">Make a ranged Gravitation attack against the Physical defense of that target, rolling 2d4 impact damage. The size of these damage dice increases with your ranks in Gravitation; at 2 ranks, roll 2d6 (instead of 2d4), and so on.</p>",
